, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Cache class with a lock.\n\n```\nparam cache\n\nactual cache.\n\nparam lock\n\nlock (context manager) to use\n```\n\nThe locked layer should be the last one before the actual cache.\n\n% code-block: python\n%\n% import threading\n% import cachetools as ct\n% import CacheToolsUtils as ctu\n% cache = ctu.LockedCache(ct.LFUCache(), threading.RLock())\n"]}, {"name": "CacheToolsUtils.PrefixedCache", "bases": ["_KeyMutMapMix", "_StatsMix", "MutableMapping"], "methods": [{"name": "CacheToolsUtils.PrefixedCache.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "cache", "type": {"name": "MutableMapping", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.MutableMapping", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "prefix", "type": {"name": "str|bytes", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "CacheToolsUtils.PrefixedCache._key", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Cache class to add a key prefix.\n\n```\nparam cache\n\nactual cache.\n\nparam prefix\n\nprefix to prepend to keys.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "CacheToolsUtils.StatsCache", "bases": ["_MutMapMix", "MutableMapping"], "methods": [{"name": "CacheToolsUtils.StatsCache.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "cache", "type": {"name": "MutableMapping", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.MutableMapping", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "return